    <h1>Sip on SU&#xAD;PER&#x27;s new of&#xAD;fer&#xAD;ings</h1>
    <h2></h2>
    <section>
        <a href="/singapore/the-straits-times/textview" title="The Straits Times">The Straits Times</a>
        - <a href="/singapore/the-straits-times/20201228/textview" title="The Straits Times - 2020-12-28"><time>2020-12-28</time></a>
        - <span>SINGAPORE</span>
        - <span role="byline"></span>
    </section>

    <p>SU­PER, a pi­o­neer in cof­fee, tea and ce­real in­stant mixes, has un­veiled a new re­vamped look across its port­fo­lio — one of the many steps the brand is tak­ing to ap­peal to the mod­ern con­sumer and stay rel­e­vant for gen­er­a­tions to come.</p>
    <p>SU­PER prod­ucts will now fea­ture an up­dated ver­sion of its well-recog­nised logo. Their pack­ag­ing de­sign has also been sim­pli­fied to cre­ate a more dis­tinct look and feel.</p>
    <p>New­est ad­di­tion to SU­PER’s cof­fee range — which in­cludes their Reg­u­lar Range and White Cof­fee Range — is the SU­PER Zero Sugar Added 2-in-1 Cof­fee, which de­liv­ers SU­PER’s sig­na­ture cof­fee aroma and smooth­ness with­out added sugar.</p>
    <p>For more in­for­ma­tion, please visit https://www.face­book.com/su­per­sin­ga­pore or their In­sta­gram page: @su­per_sin­ga­pore</p>

